title: Alan Tsarayev
text:
Alan Albertovich Tsarayev (; born 1 June 1999) is a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who plays for <a href="FC%20Alania%20Vladikavkaz%20%282019%29">FC Alania Vladikavkaz</a>.
Club career.
He made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> for <a href="FC%20Alania%20Vladikavkaz%20%282019%29">FC Alania Vladikavkaz</a> on 1 August 2020 in a game against <a href="FC%20SKA-Khabarovsk">FC SKA-Khabarovsk</a>, he substituted <a href="Alan%20Khugayev%20%28footballer%29">Alan Khugayev</a> in the 55th minute.
Personal life.
His father <a href="Albert%20Tsarayev">Albert Tsarayev</a> also played football professionally.
